{
  "description": "A large, whimsical sculpture constructed from driftwood and found objects stands on a grey, pebbled beach. The sculpture is humanoid in form, with outstretched arms and a detailed, textured surface covered in colorful items like glass bottles, painted boards, and fabric. A child wearing a red jacket and jeans stands in front of the sculpture, facing the camera. Behind the sculpture is a wide expanse of calm, grey water, and in the distance, a bridge or pier and several tall communication towers can be seen. The sky is overcast and grey. The overall scene suggests a creative, artistic installation in a natural setting.",
